{{- range .EntryPoints }}
- "{{.Name}}" → role_pair: "{{.RolePair}}", type: "{{.TaskType}}" (dispatches to {{.DisplayName}})
{{- end }}

CLASSIFICATION GUIDANCE:
- Choose "detailed-spec" if the document is already a detailed specification with structured
  requirements or a list of user stories. The document must be unambiguously implementation-ready.
- Choose "general-objective" for vision documents, broad objectives, or when uncertain.
  Default to "general-objective" — skipping the spec phase is riskier than redundant refinement.

After classifying, write a JSON file with the chosen role_pair and run liza add-tasks.
